6. Collapse Mode Protocol

(UPRR + OSIIN)

For when shit really hits the fan: internet down, grids failing, institutions gone.

Trigger when:

Internet unreliable or gone

Grid unstable

Supply chains broken

Central services dead


Tools / Behaviors:

Offline UPRR:

Paper or local-only ledger for resources.


Manual OSIIN Logs:

Write down designs, fixes, failures.


Radio-based Sync:

Use HAM / walkie systems to coordinate with nearby nodes.


Repair Guild Activation:

Community repair parties become priority.


P2P Fabrication:

Local making replaces external supply.




